TI  - Testing a model of turnover intention: Lecturers at the University of Namibia
T2  - SA JOURNAL OF HUMAN RESOURCE MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - basic psychological need satisfaction
KW  - organisational commitment
KW  - job embeddedness
KW  - work engagement
