TI  - The effects of openness, altruism and instructional self-efficacy on work engagement of MOOC instructors
T2  - BRITISH JOURNAL OF EDUCATIONAL TECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - JOB-PERFORMANCE
KW  - TEACHER BURNOUT
KW  - PERSONALITY
KW  - REPRESENTATIONS
